  "description": [
    "Jr W Keheler Cites Correct Figures On August 28 Dem ocratic candidate for First Selectman Daniel Hag earty accused his opponent Edmund JKel eher of issuing false state ments concerning the tax reform in Newington Hagearty stated that Kel eher had listed interest charges as 32830 when in actuality the 1960 tax report listed the charges as 49171 Civil Defense Organization In Newington This week the Town Crier continues its interview with Mr Earl Kemmler Dir ector of Civil Defense in Newington How well prepared is Newington for a nuclear attack Last week in dividual preparedness was discussed As stated by Mr Kemmler there is great apathy and skep ticism among the public about preparedness but the organization of Civil De fense is not apathetic In Newington all positions from the Director on down to a Rescue Warden are on a volunteer basis and comprised of a hard core of loyal workers In addi tion to the Director there is a Deputy Director Op erations Officer Com munications Officer Radio Officer Chief of Radio logical Defense Chief Rescue Warden Chief and Deputy Chief of Auxiliary Fire Service Chief and Deputy Chief of Auxiliary Police Service Chief of Transportation Service Chief"
